info.name: 【Stopped Updating】Dribbble Dark Mode
info.description: CSS has exceeded the limit. Dribbble Dark has stopped updating. Thank the 285 people who have used this style. Dribbble Dark Mode Dribbble Dark Mode gives Dribbble a darker look for a better viewing experience and makes it easier to focus on the shots you're watching. Features: - Dark Mode - Support the brand new dribbble design - Colorful style theme - Block Ads - Stay updated until Dribbble launches the official dark mode. Note: Please feel free to tell me if anything isn't properly, the problem will soon be resolved.
